jot.util

Class CoreGameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • jot.math.geometry.TransformGroup
      • jot.util.CoreGameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Node, Transformable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GameObject

    public abstract class CoreGameObject
extends TransformGroup
    Abstract class that each generic game object class, each corresponding to a game state, must extend.
    Author:
    G. Amador & A. Gomes
